article.story: NACOGDOCHES, Texas -- — Jalil Beaubrun's 22 points helped Stephen F. Austin defeat Utah Valley 77-72 on Thursday night. Beaubrun added eight rebounds for the 'Jacks (13-8, 6-4 Western Athletic Conference). Latrell Jossell added 19 points while shooting 5 for 11 (1 for 4 from 3-point range) and 8 of 10 from the free throw line, and he also had three steals. Kyle Hayman had 14 points and was 5 of 14 shooting, including 1 for 3 from 3-point range, and went 3 for 4 from the line. The Wolverines (9-12, 4-6) were led by Tanner Toolson and Caleb Stone-Carrawell with 20 points apiece. In addition, Ethan Potter finished with 15 points and seven rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
